{"tid":1383803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對付分化 最重要唔係滅聲","createTime":"2019-07-29T18:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:10:31.000Z","uid":282134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"815763722041870373148dfb0325ea0d815aefa7","tid":1383803,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:43:10.000Z","msg":"對付分化，三毛侵入 冷處理或者滅聲各樣野都只係一種方法 我地最需要最重要嘅係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">思考</span></span> <br />\n去思考對方嘅意見對我地一直以來<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">追求緊嘅目標有咩影響</span>，係行近一步定遠一步，唔好一來就否定/支持，最重要係經過思考 睇深一層個意思。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係當我地場運動成功左都只會好快俾中央搞返掂。<br />\n<br />\n爭取制度改革嘅時候唔好忘記自己思想上有咩可以進步嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n因為去到最後，制度好易俾人侵蝕，只有思想係可以繼承落去<br />\n<br />\n無論場運動成唔成功，只要有香港人嘅地方，我地就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">永不放棄追求自由</span></span>"},{"pid":"c694ae1e080e1ad7872c91cb0314642db8141584","tid":1383803,"uid":41490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:46:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=bac5506e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a>"},{"pid":"8f3de71583d2417a88e8baa71a5e8b9e31b9b647","tid":1383803,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:48:32.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"ba520fe0691bcbb4b4361eb643abd56c1a0a72d3","tid":1383803,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"互相提點"},{"pid":"c44b1e4c6